{"tid":2143692,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你信不信柒婆？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T11:54:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c67327c6326761ef8cdb38b84961244726e4e12d","tid":2143692,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/WFV2DDKEFNCLHPIXAJS2LOPPZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FWFV2DDKEFNCLHPIXAJS2LOPPZE%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=333d8a24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200722%2FWFV2DDKEFNCLHPIXAJS2LOPPZE%2F&h=50bf8025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200722/WFV2DDKEFNCLHPIXAJS2LOPPZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n你信不信柒婆？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I-zxp3aIz9OG2i-9CFqkZzpIxG4=/6522x4276/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJI2ZHMAGZAJVDCP4KYPTFDGMA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI-zxp3aIz9OG2i-9CFqkZzpIxG4%3D%2F6522x4276%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJI2ZHMAGZAJVDCP4KYPTFDGMA.JPG&h=282d259b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在專業人士一片反對聲中，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n整件事說不出的反智，明明是不封關、免檢疫引致香港出現武漢肺炎第三波，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測核酸，檢測的究竟是病毒的核酸，還是被檢測者的核酸？檢測結果會送去甚麼地方，做甚麼用途？柒婆出來拍胸口說檢測結果不會送中。你相信嗎？一個說過不會參選特首但最終成為特首的女人，一個承諾若香港人主流意見令她無法再擔任特首便會辭職，但迄今戀棧權位、賴死不走的女人，誠信早已破產。她說的話，你選擇信，還是不信？<br />\n<br />\n此次為香港人做核酸檢測的機構，包括與華大基因有關的實驗室。而華大基因旗下兩間企業，涉嫌參與強制對新疆維族人採集DNA而遭美國財政部列入制裁名單。這樣一個機構來為香港人做完全沒有必要的核酸檢測，香港人能放心嗎？"},{"pid":"6d2d9af2b428246e694081abfa5794937530a0e3","tid":2143692,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"Push <i